{%- comment -%}
  worker-lowstock · "Quedan pocas" (shopify-control). Bloque Custom Liquid en la ficha,
  cerca del precio. Lee product.metafields.worker.lowstock (umbral + texto) y el stock
  REAL de la variante. Solo aparece si hay tracking de stock y quedan entre 1 y el
  umbral — nunca inventa un número. Guard: COSMETIC_METAFIELDS.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign ls = product.metafields.worker.lowstock.value -%}
{%- if ls and ls.threshold -%}
  {%- assign v = product.selected_or_first_available_variant -%}
  {%- if v.inventory_management and v.inventory_quantity > 0 and v.inventory_quantity <= ls.threshold -%}
<div id="worker-lowstock" class="wls">
  <span class="wls-dot">🔥</span>
  {{ ls.text | default: 'Quedan pocas unidades' | escape }}
  <b>({{ v.inventory_quantity }})</b>
</div>
<style>
  #worker-lowstock.wls{ font-family:inherit; color:#b45; font-size:13px; font-weight:600;
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; margin:12px 0; }
  #worker-lowstock b{ color:#4B4B4B; }
</style>
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
